      "props": {
        "content": "**Shape (alignment)** \u2014 25 nodes total. `interview`, `brainstorming` (superseded), `prior-art`, `cass`, `cdo`, `arch`, `cass-memory`, `codebase-archaeology`, `skill-discovery`, `lev-research`, `sherlock`, `search`, `product-manager`, `ux-researcher`, `information-architect`. External: omx-01/02, ooo-01/03/11, omo-01.\n\n**Plan (crystallization)** \u2014 19 nodes. `planning-workflow`, `writing-plans`, `lev-plan`, `arch`, `lev-cdo`, `cdo-team`, `lev-align`, `review-queue`, `lev-roadmap`, `lev-sdlc`, `work`, `validate`. External: omx-05, ooo-05/10.\n\n**Deliver (execution)** \u2014 32 nodes. `executing-plans`, `subagent-driven-development`, `dispatching-parallel-agents`, `multi-agent-swarm-workflow`, `test-driven-development`, `systematic-debugging`, `multi-pass-bug-hunting`, `autodev-loop`, `simplify`, `ntm`, `agent-browser`, `lev-workshop`, `vibing-with-ntm`. External: omx-03/04/06/09, omc-01/03, ooo-07/08/09, omo-02, hm-03.\n\n**Close (validation)** \u2014 26 nodes. `verification-before-completion`, `requesting-code-review`, `receiving-code-review`, `codebase-audit`, `ubs`, `handoff`, `lev-align`, `de-slopify`, `finishing-a-development-branch`, `changelog-md-workmanship`, `readme-writing`. External: ooo-04/06, omc-02, omx-07, omo-03, hm-02, oc-01/02."
